===================================================
MARS - Metereological Archive and Retrieval System
===================================================

An updated version of the install instructions can also be found at
http://software.ecmwf.int/wiki/display/MARSAD/Building+MARS+with+CMake

=============
QUICK INSTALL
=============

1. Extract the source files

 tar zxvf MarsServer-7.1.0-Source.tar.gz -C /path/to/src

2. Use cmake and point the module path to the installed source.

 cmake /path/to/src [...]
